verbose_text: Of note, 18 h after the ICV injection of LPS, the number of Iba-1-positive cells did not increase significantly in Plexin-A1-/- mice compared with WT mice (XREF_FIG), and there was no significant increase in inflammation related mediators such as COX-2, IL-1beta, TNF-alpha and iNOS (XREF_FIG).
evidence: inflammation-related mediators such as COX-2, IL-1beta
